1
00:00:02,406 --> 00:00:05,596
Hello. Were you at the butcher's?
你好. 刚才你在肉店里吗?

2
00:00:06,469 --> 00:00:07,835
Yes. I was.
是的, 我在肉店里.

3
00:00:08,772 --> 00:00:11,458
Were you at the butcher's, too?
你也在肉店里吗?

4
00:00:11,923 --> 00:00:13,905
No, I wasn't.
不, 我不是.

5
00:00:14,588 --> 00:00:17,517
I was at the greengrocer's.
我在蔬菜水果店里.

6
00:00:18,222 --> 00:00:19,534
How's Jimmy today?
Jimmy今天怎么样?

7
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:23,456
He's very well, thank you.
他很好, 谢谢你.

8
00:00:24,618 --> 00:00:27,905
Was he absent from school last week?
上星期他没上学吧?

9
00:00:28,804 --> 00:00:29,951
Yes, he was.
是的, 他没上学.

10
00:00:31,467 --> 00:00:37,763
He was absent on Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday.
他星期一, 星期二, 星期三和星期四没去上学.

11
00:00:39,015 --> 00:00:41,063
How are you all keeping?
你们身体都好吗?

12
00:00:41,808 --> 00:00:43,126
Very well, thank you.
很好, 谢谢你.

13
00:00:44,586 --> 00:00:48,673
We're going to spend three days in the country.
我们打算到乡下去三天.

14
00:00:49,673 --> 00:00:53,897
We're going to stay at my mother's for the weekend.
在我母亲家度周末.

15
00:00:55,381 --> 00:00:59,577
Friday, Saturday and Sunday in the country!
星期五, 星期六和星期日在乡下过!

16
00:01:00,686 --> 00:01:02,853
Aren't you lucky!
你们真幸运啊!

